    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an automotive specimen of peerless quality. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, reflecting a standard of maintenance that borders on obsessive. Every surface, mechanical component, and aesthetic detail has been preserved to an exacting degree. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine example of engineering excellence.",
